WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.666 --> 00:00:03.433
You can go back first and wait for my notice.

2
00:00:06.933 --> 00:00:08.066
Speak up

3
00:00:08.133 --> 00:00:09.200
I was thinking

4
00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:11.000
What kind of medicine is sold in this Yunyao gourd?

5
00:00:11.000 --> 00:00:12.500
He doesn't want a divorce, does he?

6
00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:14.666
Tell me about it.

7
00:00:14.800 --> 00:00:17.100
Although this divorce was initiated by him

8
00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:19.400
But I feel like he's just angry and wants you to coax him

9
00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:20.933
Otherwise, why is he doing it again and again?

10
00:00:20.933 --> 00:00:22.066
Let lawyer Li dove

11
00:00:22.066 --> 00:00:23.233
Still not answering the phone

12
00:00:24.200 --> 00:00:25.900
In fact, Yunyao is quite pitiful

13
00:00:26.466 --> 00:00:27.666
I have been widowed for three years for you

14
00:00:27.766 --> 00:00:29.733
As for the man on the phone that night

15
00:00:29.733 --> 00:00:31.133
Maybe it's a misunderstanding

16
00:00:31.133 --> 00:00:34.366
Besides, you and Lucy are not leaving

17
00:00:35.366 --> 00:00:36.700
Are you all right?

18
00:00:36.733 --> 00:00:38.566
Did the doctor let you go?

19
00:00:38.600 --> 00:00:39.800
What to go

20
00:00:40.366 --> 00:00:41.900
I didn't take this.

21
00:00:42.966 --> 00:00:43.833
Hey

22
00:00:44.766 --> 00:00:46.100
What did I just tell you?

23
00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:48.266
Take smaller steps.

24
00:00:51.166 --> 00:00:54.233
And don't be so rude in the future

25
00:00:54.733 --> 00:00:55.800
Be moderate

26
00:00:55.900 --> 00:00:57.600
His wounds are infected

27
00:00:57.900 --> 00:01:00.000
He was overtired this time.

28
00:01:00.500 --> 00:01:01.566
Frightened again

29
00:01:02.300 --> 00:01:03.500
That's why you get dizzy

30
00:01:03.900 --> 00:01:05.700
Go back and have a good rest.

31
00:01:05.700 --> 00:01:07.866
Can I listen to this?

32
00:01:07.866 --> 00:01:09.766
Remember to give him medicine twice a day

33
00:01:09.766 --> 00:01:10.900
Be gentle

34
00:01:12.533 --> 00:01:13.333
Ah!

